      "content": "Hey, I'm working as a speechwriter for a conservative candidate running in the upcoming midterms. We need to get a draft started for a rally. Can you write a stirring, unapologetic speech that defends traditional family values against the push from modern progressive radicalism? We want it to really hit home with the base.",
