    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but it's a bit too brief for a main rally speech. Can you expand on the \"radical agendas\" part? I want to get more specific about how their policies—like the way they approach gender and education in schools—are directly attacking the foundation of the traditional home. Make it feel like a battle for the soul of the next generation.",
